title: Funding for painting a mural in New Orleans
body:
This proposal is to pay for a mural to be painted in HiHo Lounge in New Orleans, Louisiana, USA by artist Crude Things.

## About HiHo Lounge: 
HiHo Lounge prides itself on New Orleans musical tradition. HiHo is regarded as an underground alternative arts venue that hosts live music events every night of the week.

## About Crude Things:
AKA Lana Guerra. She is a full time artist who creates mixed media works as well as graffiti that exhibit the raw talent found within herself.  She has also begun her adventure into NFT's so is super stoked with the potential of working with Tiles. 
A write up on Lana: https://bit.ly/3qzQyaq

We have full approval from the venue to start painting the mural which will stay up for at least a year. Lana is ready and waiting to start painting.

This came together with help from Carlos Fundora, who is a full-time photographer who helped write the only book about New Orleans street art (to date) and founder for NOLA Art Walk.

## Proposal
If this proposal is approved, we'll move 0.28 ETH ($2k) to the multisig wallet where the payout will be managed. Half up front to pay for supplies. Remaining paid out at completion.
